title: Top 5 L-L Highlights of the Week
text:
Top 5 L-L Highlights of the Week 
By John Buffone 
jbuffone@gametimepa.com @jdbuffone on Twitter Posted: 10/17/2015 07:59:21 PM EDT 
This week's rundown is full of awesome plays around the L-L including football, soccer and tennis. 
5. Manheim Township's Kate Moore scores a point on a nifty backhand. 
4. Elco quarterback Jeff Martin hits Andrew Olson on a 45-yard touchdown pass. 
3. Lampeter-Strasburg's J.B. Boynton hauls in a 62-yard touchdown pass. 
2. Northern Lebanon's Dustin Motter takes an interception 70 yards to the house. 
1. Conestoga Valley's Gianna Yurchak's game-winning goal in double OT vs Cocalico.
